WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.400
To  engage  your  sports  club  community,  start  by  attracting  fans  on  major  social  media  platforms

2
00:00:05.400 --> 00:00:07.980
and  identifying  your  most  enthusiastic  supporters.

3
00:00:08.280 --> 00:00:13.620
Once  you  know  who  your  super  fans  are,  invite  them  into  our  dedicated  app,  a  private  hub  like  Discord

4
00:00:13.620 --> 00:00:14.920
built  for  everyday  fans.

5
00:00:15.220 --> 00:00:20.500
Inside,  they  scroll  through  a  feed  of  club -exclusive  videos  and  posts  with  a  TikTok -style  experience.

6
00:00:29.247 --> 00:00:33.847
They can see where other members are on a social map, join chat channels for match days

7
00:00:33.847 --> 00:00:37.747
or topics, and create groups for regions, supporter clubs, or events.

8
00:00:37.967 --> 00:00:43.247
You  can  share  exclusive  content,  manage  discussions,  and  keep  fans  engaged  without  algorithms

9
00:00:43.247 --> 00:00:43.527
getting

10
00:00:44.167 --> 00:00:49.087
This mobile app gives you a single place to own your community, deliver content, and build

11
00:00:49.087 --> 00:00:50.807
deeper relationships with your fans.

12
00:00:52.107 --> 00:00:56.147
Behind every cheer, every comment, every view, there's real fans.

13
00:00:56.214 --> 00:00:57.294
and activity driving it.

14
00:00:57.414 --> 00:00:59.814
This dashboard brings that to life in real time.

15
00:01:00.094 --> 00:01:03.834
Here, you can see the AI Assistant Surface Key Insights

16
00:01:03.834 --> 00:01:06.534
instantly, the most recently signed in fans,

17
00:01:06.794 --> 00:01:08.234
total members in each group,

18
00:01:08.414 --> 00:01:10.694
and the latest five fans joining the platform.

19
00:01:11.134 --> 00:01:13.734
Every query runs live, no code needed,

20
00:01:14.014 --> 00:01:16.334
giving you clear visibility into who's active

21
00:01:16.334 --> 00:01:17.794
and how your community is growing.

22
00:01:26.301 --> 00:01:31.201
And when you're ready to expand, you can invite new fans directly through email, bringing

23
00:01:31.201 --> 00:01:33.421
them into your private platform with just one click.

24
00:01:33.681 --> 00:01:38.381
It's the simplest way for sports marketers to understand engagement, track growth, and

25
00:01:38.381 --> 00:01:40.781
keep fans connected in one place they truly belong.
